Package com.kroy.game

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Assets  
    BarManager
    Class created by Septagon Used to give the engines a health bar and a water meter so the stats can be seen easier
    Bullet
    Class that is used to create animations when the engines and fortresses are attacking each other
    Character
    Character class used as a base class for all moveable objects in the game
    Constants
    File used to store all the constants in the game
    Enemy
    Used to handle all info about patrols and fortresses
    FireEngine
    Used to handle all the info about fire engines in the game
    Fortress
    Used to handle all the info about the Fortresses in the game
    HighlightMap  
    Human
    Class used to manage the fireEngines and all the users info
    MainClass
    Class to bring all elements of the game together
    Map
    Used to load in the map and handle all the tiles of the game
    Patrol  
    Player
    Base class used for handling info about a player
    SceneManager
    Used to handle all the scenes in the game and to allow you to swap between different scenes at any time
    Station
    Class used to handle info about the fireStation
    Tile
    Used to handle info about each of the tiles in the game
    Tooltip
    Used to create tooltips which are used to give info on the stats of the item you are currently on
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Character.Type  
    SceneType
    Enum that stores the different possible scenes the game could be in
    TileType
    Enum storing the different types of tile that are present in the game
